desc_short	-----								Spellbind is an adventure-puzzle game that follows Luppe, a 16-year old boy who happens to be the head of the biggest street gang in the small town of Riathon. You’ve been challenged by your archrival, Ricko, to steal the most expensive bottle of wine in the cellar of Lord Amatar.							
developer									Spider Key Games								
